Class VarFramingMatcher

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.fge.grappa.matchers.wrap.VarFramingMatcher
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Matcher, GraphNode<Matcher>, Rule

    public final class VarFramingMatcher
extends Object
implements Matcher
    Special wrapping matcher that manages the creation and destruction of execution frames for a number of action vars.
